Sterling K. Brown won the Emmy for best actor in a drama for his performance in NBC&#8217;s breakout family drama &#8220;This Is Us,&#8221; which tells of the relationship between triplets and their parents over a three-decade period.It was the second Emmy in as many years for Brown, who won a supporting actor award last year for his role as a lawyer in &#8220;The People vs. O.J. Simpson: American Crime Story.&#8221;-AFP